  <brief_title>The Postoperative Analgesic Effect of Combination With Dexmedetomidine in Fentanyl-based Intravenous Patient Controlled Analgesia Compared With Conventional Thoracic Epidural and Intravenous Patient Controlled Analgesia After Radical Open Gastrectomy</brief_title>
