  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study to test hypothesis that addition of dexmedetomidine to fentanyl based
      intravenous patient controlled analgesia (PCA) improves postoperative pain compared with
      conventional thoracic epidural and intravenous patient controlled analgesia after radical
      open gastrectomy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
